About
-----
A PHP library which helps working with WKHTMLTOPDF <http://code.google.com/p/wkhtmltopdf/>

Author
------
Aurimas Baubkus aka aur1mas <aur1mas@devnet.lt>
Released under "New BSD license"

Usage
-----
<?php
    try {
        $wkhtmltopdf = new Core_Wkhtmltopdf(array('path' => APPLICATION_PATH . '/../public/uploads/'));
        $wkhtmltopdf->setTitle("Title");
        $wkhtmltopdf->setHtml("Content");
        $wkhtmltopdf->output(Wkhtmltopdf::MODE_DOWNLOAD, "file.pdf");
    } catch (Exception $e) {
        echo $e->getMessage();
    }
?>
On Gist: https://gist.github.com/733109

